 drivers/phy/qualcomm/phy-qcom-qmp-usb.c       | 188 ++++++++---------
 drivers/phy/qualcomm/phy-qcom-qmp-usbc.c      | 180 ++++++++--------
 5 files changed, 405 insertions(+), 405 deletions(-)

